---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - Sunshine Maids"
  description="Sunshine Maids LLC Terms of Service. Learn about our service agreements, policies, and customer responsibilities."
  canonical="/terms-of-service"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block bg-coral/10 text-coral font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-5">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-light text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Please read these terms carefully before booking our cleaning services.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-light/70 text-sm mt-4">Effective Date: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-14 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-text-light">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4">Service Description</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Sunshine Maids LLC provides residential and commercial cleaning services in the Austin metro area. Our services include but are not limited to: basic house cleaning, deep cleaning, move-in/move-out cleaning, recurring maid services, Airbnb/vacation rental cleaning, commercial cleaning, and post-construction cleaning.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Booking and Cancellation</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong>Booking:</strong> To schedule a cleaning, contact us by phone, through our website contact form, or via Telegram. We will confirm your appointment within 24 hours.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6">
          <strong>Cancellation:</strong> We require at least 24 hours' notice for cancellations or rescheduling. Cancellations made with less than 24 hours notice may incur a fee. No-shows will be charged the full service amount.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Pricing and Payment</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong>Pricing:</strong> Service pricing depends on the size of the property, type of cleaning, condition of the space, and frequency of service. We provide free estimates for all services.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6">
          <strong>Payment:</strong> Payment is due at the time of service. We accept cash, credit/debit cards, Zelle, and Venmo. For recurring clients, we may offer invoicing arrangements.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Independent Contractors</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Sunshine Maids LLC serves as a service platform that connects customers with independent cleaning professionals. All cleaning professionals are independent contractors and are not employees of Sunshine Maids LLC. Each cleaner is responsible for their own taxes, insurance, and compliance with applicable laws.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Insurance and Liability</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Sunshine Maids LLC is fully insured and bonded. In the unlikely event of damage to your property during our service, we will work with you to resolve the matter. Damage claims must be reported within 24 hours of service completion. Our insurance coverage is designed to protect against property damage caused by our cleaning professionals.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Property Access and Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong>Access:</strong> Customers are responsible for providing access to the property. If providing a key or access code, we recommend using a secure lockbox or alternative secure method.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6">
          <strong>Security:</strong> Our cleaning professionals are background-checked. However, customers should secure valuables, jewelry, and sensitive documents before each cleaning appointment.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Damage Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          In the event of damage caused by our cleaning professionals:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Report the damage within 24 hours of service completion</li>
          <li>Provide photographs and documentation of the damage</li>
          <li>We will investigate and work with our insurance provider to resolve claims</li>
          <li>Resolution will be based on the circumstances and our insurance coverage</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Satisfaction Guarantee</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We are committed to your satisfaction. If you are not happy with our service, contact us within 24 hours and we will return to re-clean any areas that do not meet your expectations at no additional charge. This guarantee applies to regularly scheduled cleaning services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Customer Responsibilities</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide accurate information about your property</li>
          <li>Ensure access to the property at scheduled time</li>
          <li>Secure valuables and sensitive items</li>
          <li>Report any special cleaning requirements or concerns in advance</li>
          <li>Provide 24 hours' notice for cancellations or rescheduling</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Service Limitations</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We reserve the right to refuse service if:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>The property is hazardous or unsafe</li>
          <li>Conditions make cleaning impossible or unsafe</li>
          <li>There is evidence of infestations or biohazards</li>
          <li>Payment is not provided at time of service (for new clients)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Modifications to Terms</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. Your continued use of our services after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Texas. Any disputes arising from these terms or our services shall be resolved in the courts of Travis County, Texas.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-4 mt-10">Contact Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If you have any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> hello@sunshinemaids.com</li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> (512) 555-0147</li>
          <li><strong>Address:</strong> 1847 South Lamar Blvd, Austin, TX 78704</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-14 md:py-20 bg-coral">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Book Your Cleaning?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Let us take care of your home so you can enjoy your free time.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-coral px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5">
          Book My Free Estimate
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+14059774237" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-coral transition-colors duration-200">
          Call (512) 555-0147
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
